==English==
===Etymology===
From [[Ancient Greek]] '''[[κίνημα]]''' (''kinema'') "movement", from '''[[κινέω]]''' (''kineo'') "to move, to put in motion".

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''cinema'''
#A [[film]] or [[movie]] [[theatre]]
#Films or movies as a [[group]], or the film / movie [[industry]]
#The [[art]] of making films / movies
